Package org.unc.lac.baboon.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BadPolicyException  
    BadTopicsJsonFormat
    This exception is thrown when the given topics json file format is invalid.
    InvalidGuardProviderMethod
    This exception is thrown when a method annotated with GuardProvider has parameters on its declaration or if its return type is not boolean
    MultipleGuardProvidersException
    This exception is thrown when more than one method of the same class are declared as GuardProviders for the same guard name
    NoTopicsJsonFileException
    This exception is thrown when the given topics json file can not be found on the filesystem.
    NotSubscribableException
    This exception is thrown when the system can not subscribe an object and method to a topic.
